examples.text: I want to eat isaw and siomai
The isaw in diliman tho ... all hail food !

relations.target: Filipino: official language of the Philippines; based on Tagalog; draws its lexicon from other Philippine languages <i73061>
food: any solid substance (as opposed to liquid) that is used as a source of nourishment; 'food and drink' <i76470>

senses.definition: a street food from the Philippines, made from barbecued pig or chicken intestines [Wikipedia]
